---
title: Tex-Mex Turkey Hash with Chipotle Mayo
description: Fancy some breakfast vibes for dinner tonight? Potatoes, poblanos, corn and tomatoes are roasted to achieve beautiful caramelization before getting tossed with turkey, onions and spices to create a heavenly hash.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poelee-de-dinde-tex-mex-174b4df8.jpg
